Everything must feed one merged timeline.

Your timeline must include:
	•	ORA-12805
	•	domain reconfig start/end
	•	attach/detach
	•	slave death/fatal trace
	•	IPC/network/OS anomaly
	•	service start/stop/relocate
	•	PDB open/close
	•	monitoring query execution
